信所有人都认同一点：溯源是严肃的科学问题，应由全球科学家合作开展。但是，一段时间以来，美方一些人罔顾科学和事实，鼓吹让情报机构开展调查，现在更是向国际科学界伸出“黑手”，试图迫使科学家在其霸权、霸凌、胁迫面前低头、转向。这是对科学精神的违背和侵犯，是对全球溯源合作的干扰和破坏，是对人类正义的挑战和亵渎。美方这种将溯源政治化的做法既不道德，也不得人心，终将以失败告终。 我们再次敦促美方立即停止对溯源问题的政治操弄，收回伸向科学界的“黑手”，本着科学、透明的态度，邀请世卫专家赴美开展溯源研究，就德特里克堡和美在全球设立的200多个生物实验室情况作出负责任的说明。（人民日报）"},"attached_info":"Cj8IsqztruTa/KRDEAMaCDY2NDE5MjU5ILzP54YGMD44tgtAJnIJNDY4NjI3MzcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"29 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d9a025c4519ae8178d66e61caff8748b_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1624975593.3077507","card_id":"Q_29988339","target":{"id":29988339,"title":"哪些牌子的哪些东西你用过后再也不考虑其他牌子的了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/29988339","type":"question","created":1430356423,"answer_count":2686,"follower_count":122572,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[276,307,843,1309,1761],"comment_count":59,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"现在问题下较多回答都是化妆/护肤品相关，希望能有更多不同的回答"},"attached_info":"Cj4IsqztruTa/KRDEAMaBzQxNzc4MDYgx4OGqgUwOzjMvQdAJ3IIMjk5ODgzMzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"28 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-adda1edebd2394578282b4f198bb67bb_hd.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1624975593.3082254","card_id":"Q_467187752","target":{"id":467187752,"title":"理科女，去复旦还是交大？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/467187752","type":"question","created":1624539786,"answer_count":157,"follower_count":792,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[7091,8342,10012],"comment_count":36,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"高考江苏前200。没有对某专业有特别强烈的兴趣。希望了解一下这两个学校的宿舍、食堂、学习氛围，感谢各位！ 2021.6.25添